{"tid":1358551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［人手置頂］就咁放過石鏡泉，唔係呀嘛？？","createTime":"2019-07-24T03:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T08:24:36.000Z","uid":258521,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"4f2e476b938a831722043049546d8d4da95ca9c4","tid":1358551,"uid":258521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:02:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ApRMMVt1ksg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FApRMMVt1ksg&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1YgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=af99266b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ApRMMVt1ksg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢條茂利公開叫人使用暴力已經觸犯公安條例第26條</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解完全冇人做野？冇人理？<br />\n<br />\n唔通叫牛屎佬打完人，然後係咁意道個歉， 辭個職就可以當冇事？？<br />\n<br />\n咁我係咪叫人打完你，然後道歉辭職就冇事呀？<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n26. 公眾聚集中<span style=\"color: blue;\">倡議</span>使用暴力<br />\n任何人如無合法權限而在公眾聚集中發表任何聲明，或其所作出的行為，為意圖煽惑或誘使他人作出以下作為，或為其明知或應該知道相當可能會煽惑或誘使他人作出以下作為者 &mdash;&mdash;  (由1970年第31號第15條修訂)<br />\n(a)殺死任何人或任何類別或群體的人，或傷害他們的身體；<br />\n(b)摧毀或破壞任何財產；或<br />\n(c)用武力或威嚇手段永久或暫時剝奪他人對任何財產的管有或使用，<br />\n即屬犯罪 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(i)一經循公訴程序定罪，可處監禁5年；及<br />\n(ii)一經循簡易程序定罪，可處第2級罰款及監禁2年。<br />\n(編輯修訂&mdash;&mdash;2013年第1號編輯修訂紀錄)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EVB11RV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVB11RV.jpg&h=44ab02ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap245!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap245%21zh-Hant-HK&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1YgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=46eb4192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap245!zh-Hant-HK</a>"},{"pid":"a6cc8d67532e3c046c66f1046ff5d7b4e4625424","tid":1358551,"uid":165246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:03:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中 下落不明<br />\n要求公佈義士下落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"fe589bbde4b68c8f72fe56a5257e4b409acd5d17","tid":1358551,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"唔可以放過佢"},{"pid":"7a4b1001d36faa4abbfd4697ed1f9877101bc19b","tid":1358551,"uid":258521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:06:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ff30f31604dccb8e4d516d45643775758d2b0ad","tid":1358551,"uid":45320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:07:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64b3d574cce79b360bc8b0c3f0cab021cc91ad2a","tid":1358551,"uid":258521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:07:18.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門"},{"pid":"2a6b4dc33f979aad157af99a27a6dc1e6ab3a401","tid":1358551,"uid":258521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b